{"tid":709242,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲試過腸動力不足","createTime":"2018-06-20T00:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T18:20:45.000Z","uid":106810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2f5803b4edd8cdcece9a51d8055843d956fda6","tid":709242,"uid":106810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:16:20.000Z","msg":"返新工壓力大，多出去食，成個星期無屎痾<br />\n<br />\n之後食返菜同生果都無效，反而肚大左<br />\n<br />\n睇醫生食d通便藥(甘油都試過) 都係痾好少<br />\n<br />\n哩排嚴重到一食野就肚脹到不得了<br />\n<br />\n上網下可能係腸動力不足<br />\n<br />\n有無經驗分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50fb3c5aea64fdcfbe30fa6e54998ef540dc922","tid":709242,"uid":164714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:17:50.000Z","msg":"我係 但我冇時間理佢 依家有個大肚腩"},{"pid":"1326da575ea67c1326ad5d66c9d457c3243717ca","tid":709242,"uid":38904,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:18:45.000Z","msg":"腸動力不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個名好似講到條腸中風噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803e8ca6db26bfe05470c569f60fe9c8cfd8b163","tid":709242,"uid":8048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:19:54.000Z","msg":"誤會咗 出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9bfacc832c15f409cdbaf68ef77aa8f1b0819c","tid":709242,"uid":39880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:23:22.000Z","msg":"肚脹再肚痛既話係可以搞到入院架<br />\n<br />\n入到去佢會幫你試下放大便<br />\n<br />\n仲放唔到就照電腦掃描睇下係塞左定點<br />\n<br />\n巴打如果有埋肚痛都唔好諗咁多入去睇下穩陣啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e5842dfeaec712e39042a6532ec32590dd07f1","tid":709242,"uid":106320,"lik