:"2018-06-20T01:13:07.000Z","msg":"食左唔得"},{"pid":"a8561e5bb2d72b1b8423592bc13be106d12ed704","tid":709242,"uid":155558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T01:21:10.000Z","msg":"營養師教：食菜唔飲水更加嚴重<br />\n<br />\n飲多啲熱水或暖水<br />\n<br />\n出戶外行返至少兩粒鐘（運動幫助大腸蠕動）<br />\n<br />\n幫助大腸蠕動水果：紅肉火龍果、奇異果、西梅（汁）<br />\n<br />\n最好順序做，飲多啲水先，跟手出去運動，最後先食水果。"},{"pid":"940e7c0c5ae93858c98040dc20fe714ca5c85966","tid":709242,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T01:23:50.000Z","msg":"你有冇女朋友？"},{"pid":"c41579a7d7279e1d65e22d4947ec990f6b0b013d","tid":709242,"uid":39880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e533a059427d7a0858b81efe9c14e50ae650d4ce","tid":709242,"uid":106810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9bfacc832c15f409cdbaf68ef77aa8f1b0819c","tid":709242,"uid":39880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:23:22.000Z","msg":"肚脹再肚痛既話係可以搞到入院架<br />\n<br />\n入到去佢會幫你試下放大便<br />\n<br />\n仲放唔到就照電腦掃描睇下係塞左定點<br />\n<br />\n巴打如果有埋肚痛都唔好諗咁多入去睇下穩陣啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:27:34.000Z","msg":"我見誇張上黎要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"果啲腸塞左咪要通番佢囉<br />\n<br />\n最壞可以係組織壞死埋要切<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過呢啲都唔關你事喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb15a7f9615ca1ec1015dde809caf0d7e3446b5","tid":709242,"uid":109263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:41:11.000Z","msg":"一路食西梅乾一路飲暖水，咁都仲係冇反應既就要去睇醫生"},{"pid":"57c72624b513d2cb579cf0ddad7b30d018ef8c07","tid":709242,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"做帶氧運動<br />\n食啲會刺激腸臟蠕動嘅食物<